ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P1: Ku shiga cikin motsi don samar da abin dogara, mai araha, samun damar duniya a lafiyar lafiya cikin minti 15 ko ƙasa.
ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P2: Saluber MD an tsara shi ne don sauya dangantakar likita-haƙuri ta hanyar samar da 24/7 zuwa ga likita a duniya.
about_us_section1_p1: SaluberMD ne kungiyar sadarwar Lafiya ta Ƙungiyar Zaɓuɓɓuka ta Ƙarfafawa don sake fasalin sabis na likita da samfurori don inganta sakamakon kiwon lafiya a dukan duniya. Ayyukan Mu na Ƙwararrun Mu na Lambobinmu, samar da damar yin amfani da lafiyar lafiyar lafiya, likitoci na kwararrun likitocin, likita na likita a cikin harsuna 18, waɗanda ba za su iya yin amfani da su ba don duba lafiyarka, da kuma samun dama ga hanyar sadarwa na masu sana'a da kuma ayyuka.
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P1:
Ta hanyar hanyar geo-localization ɗinmu app zai sami likita mafi kyau a kusa da ku. SaluberMD Dikitoci na iya ganewa, bi da su, ko tattauna yanayin lafiyar ku ta bidiyon bidiyo kuma sun ba ku tsari mai kyau. Yawancin al'amuran da suka fi dacewa da su a asibitin likita za a iya bi da su tare da ziyarar bidiyo.
Wasu daga cikin yanayin da muke bi da su:
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P2: Littafin Jakadancinka na sirri ne mai dacewa don adana duk bayanan lafiyarka, hotuna da fayiloli. Kula da lafiyarka tare da 24/7 samun damar yin amfani da duk bayanan likita naka. Ko kun kasance a gida ko tafiya kasashen waje bayaninku yana cikin ƙananan yatsa don raba tare da ma'aikacin lafiyar ku. Mai sauƙin amfani da rikodin lafiyar mutum yana samuwa a cikin harsuna 18.
ABOUT_US_SECTION3_P1: Abin sani kawai likitoci masu kyau sunyi kiwon likita kan SaluberMD. Wadannan masu sana'a sun tabbatar da su, an yi musu horo kuma sun horar da su don samar da kyakkyawan kulawa. Kowace likita yana da kwayar halitta inda za ka iya ganin tushen su, takardun shaida, da kwarewa. SaluberMD yana da ƙwarewa ga ci gaba da kulawa da kwarewar likitocinmu. Tsarin tsarin kulawa yana ba wa marasa lafiya damar likita likitoci da kuma duba likitoci duka ra'ayi.

QUALITY_INDEX_DESCRIPTION: Jiki na jiki shi ne matakin ƙarfin hali da damuwa na tunanin mutum wanda ya fuskanci damar da za a iya daidaitawa da kuma kula da halin da ake ciki. Shafin jiki na jiki yana nuna jikin mutum don daidaitawa da sauyin yanayi da ƙarfin ƙarfafawa, kulawa da sake mayar da lafiyar jiki. Kayan lafiyar jiki yana nunawa a cikin rayuwar mutane, koyo, da kuma aiki, amma har ma a cikin motsa jiki. Halin jikin mutum yana da dangantaka da ladabi amma yana da alaka da haɗin gwaninta da kuma motsa jiki. Ta hanyar hanyoyi masu dacewa da motsa jiki mai kyau, zai iya inganta lafiyar jiki a kowane bangare.

RECOMMEND_SECTION_P2: Muna kullum neman ingancin likitoci don kara wa tawagarmu mai ban mamaki. A matsayin memba na tawagarmu muna mutunta da kuma darajar waɗanda kuka sanya.

tipshealt11: Amfanin magungunan kwayoyin cutar, da rage yawan kwayoyin cholesterol, ya wuce hatsarin
tipshealt12: A cikin wani rahoto na baya-bayan nan a Lancet, masu bincike sun tabbatar da cewa amfani da rage LDL cholesterol tare da farfadowa na statin zai iya hana manyan al'ada (cututtukan zuciya, shanyewar jiki) kuma hakan bai wuce hadarin kwayoyi ba.
tipshealt13: Bisa ga masu bincike ne kawai abubuwan da suka faru masu tsanani wadanda aka nuna su da cutar ta hanyar dogon lokaci sune myopathy (a matsayin tsoka ko tsoka), sabon cututtukan ciwon sukari, kuma, mai yiwuwa, cututtukan haemorrhagic.
tipshealt2: Kodayake maganin alurar rigakafin ba zai samar da kariya ba, komai yana da daraja. Cibiyar CDC (Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka) tana bada shawara ga maganin muradin shekara-shekara don kowacce shekara 6 ko fiye. Alurar riga kafi yana da mahimmanci ga mutanen da ke fama da hadarin muradi, ciki har da
tipshealt5: Yaran yara (a ƙarƙashin shekaru 4 da sama da watanni 6)
tipshealt6: Ayyukan jiki na inganta ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya da tunani
tipshealt7: Ayyukan jiki na yau da kullum zai iya inganta aikin kwakwalwa a duk tsawon lokaci kuma ya rage hadarin damuwa.
tipshealt8: An wallafa littattafai masu yawa a kan hulɗar zumunci da kuma amfani da aikin jiki na yau da kullum da kuma ingantawa aikin aiki.
tipshealt9: Rashin rinjayar shine kai tsaye a kan kwakwalwa da kuma kai tsaye ta hanyar aiki ta jiki da kuma jiki a jiki.
